Setup instructions ---

1. cd /var
2. svn co http://svn.highgroove.com:8080/spy_client/trunk spy
3. Try running it w/o cron
   OSX:    /usr/local/bin/ruby /var/spy/bin/sspy -s spy.highgroove.com -u USERLOGIN -p USERPASS -c CLIENTID
   LINUX:  /usr/bin/ruby /var/spy/bin/sspy -s spy.highgroove.com -u USERLOGIN -p USERPASS -c CLIENTID
4. Add to etc/crontab (this is for every 10 minutes):
*/10  *  * * *  root /usr/bin/ruby /var/spy/bin/sspy -s spy.highgroove.com -u USERLOGIN -p USERPASS -c CLIENTID

If you are testing with a locally installed spy server, then you can omit the -s option. The server will default to localhost:8000.
